新聞報道 <br />\n於零晨3時有4名自稱休班警員進入 XX大廈中<br />\n搶劫了多達50戶 的財物<br />\n該50間住戶都稱因害怕警員 而讓其入內搜查 最後發現失去高達10萬的財物<br />\n整棟大廈合共損失 100萬 而警方表示 該4名並非警員<br />\n而因為警員已不用出示委任證 所以本港本年度已有達 一千宗 自稱休班警而發生的謀殺搶劫及強姦案"},{"pid":"9aeee8a5c0f05d503c645873c87b26e553c15d32","tid":1569783,"uid":51234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"全民呀sir/madam<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569861</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79152243e80e9def946b0eedecebf79f3bca3968","tid":1569783,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地係警察 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我先係呀sir<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都係wor<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喂我都係<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依到依到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個4個係假差佬真小強 同我禁住佢地! 拆裝!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地先係警察!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無證架佢地 搞佢!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif